WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.085
Pixy Williams, wahine Māori tuatahi hei kaiwaiata whetū.

2
00:00:05.085 --> 00:00:08.020
Ko Piki Te Ora tōna ingoa whānau,

3
00:00:08.020 --> 00:00:13.064
koia te kaiwaiata tuatahi i mau te reo aru moni i te mauhanga o Blue Smoke.

4
00:00:13.064 --> 00:00:16.077
Nā Rūrū Karaitiana i tito.

5
00:00:16.077 --> 00:00:24.050
I kī a Amelia i whakatipua a Pixie i Mōhaka, i kī a te whare o ana tipuna ko te whare waiata.

6
00:00:24.050 --> 00:00:29.009
Tekau mā whitu ōna tau ka nuku a Pixie ki Pōneke,

7
00:00:29.009 --> 00:00:31.094
ka tūtaki ki a Rūrū Karaitiana,

8
00:00:31.094 --> 00:00:37.042
kua puta noa atu a Blue Smoke i tuhia i te tau 1940.

9
00:00:37.042 --> 00:00:41.067
Ka whakahokia mai e te 28 Māori Batallion.

10
00:00:41.067 --> 00:00:44.086
He tino waiata mā Pixie i ngā pō o te Rātapu,

11
00:00:44.086 --> 00:00:51.091
engari kāore i mōhio i reira a Ruru Karaitiana e rapu ana he kaiwaiata mō Blue Smoke.

12
00:00:51.091 --> 00:00:55.037
Ka tono a ia ki te kapo raihana reo irirangi

13
00:00:55.037 --> 00:01:00.032
kia whakamaua a Blue Smoke ki te rēkoata ki tō rātou whare hou Hopu Reo.

14
00:01:00.032 --> 00:01:04.041
Te tuatahi i whakamaua te katoa ki Aotearoa.

15
00:01:04.041 --> 00:01:11.015
Ka tono a Pixie kia haramai ki te rīkoata i te waiata, engari kīhai ia e whakaae,

16
00:01:11.015 --> 00:01:18.097
nāwai rā ka whakaae, ka whakamaua a Blue Smoke i te tau 1949.

17
00:01:18.097 --> 00:01:23.062
Te mea tuatahi ki rō whare hopu reo i Aotearoa.

18
00:01:23.062 --> 00:01:30.028
Ko tā Amelia, ko te mahi kē mā ngā kaipūkahu, he tohu me pēhea te hopu i te reo

19
00:01:30.028 --> 00:01:35.066
ka whakawhiti ki te rīpene, ā, ka whakaputa kia rahi ngā nama hei tuku iho.

20
00:01:35.066 --> 00:01:40.039
Nā te koi o te whakaaro kiwi ka puta ai te waiata.

21
00:01:40.039 --> 00:01:47.035
Nō te tukunga i te waiata, tau ana ki te ao, mano mano ngā rekoata i hokona.

22
00:01:47.035 --> 00:01:55.048
Nā reira, hoatu a Māmā ki te rekoata e whitu ngā waiata ā - ruru me te ono mā ētahi atu kaitito waiata.

23
00:01:55.048 --> 00:02:03.081
Ka mutu i ngā tau e rua o te mahi rīkoata ki Aotearoa, ko Māmā te Pirinihi o Te Mātotoru.

24
00:02:03.081 --> 00:02:11.088
Pixy Williams, tu Māori Ki te ao.
